---
title: Podcast Picks
---

<header class="site-head" style="background-image: url(<%= image_path('cover-full.jpg') %>)">
	<div class="vertical">
		<div role='banner' class="header_typesome">
      <a class="logo--speech-bubble" href="/"><img src="<%= image_path('zadevchat.png') %>" alt="ZADevChat" /></a>
			<h1 class="blogtitle_typesome">
			<a title="ZADevChat" href='/'>
			The ZADevChat Podcast
			</a>
			</h1>
			<p class="blogdescription_typesome">
A weekly panel discussion with topics around the South African software developer community. Regular panelists are Len Weincier, Kenneth Kalmer and Kevin McKelvin.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</header>

<main class="main_typesome" role="main">
    <article class="article_typesome">
        <header class="posthreader_typesome">
          <h2 class="posttile_typesome">Podcast Picks</h2>
        </header>

        <div class="postcontent_typesome">
            <p>At the end of every episode we all get a turn to present a few <em>picks</em>. These can be serious or comical, technical or analogue, or anything else really.</p>
            <p>We hope you enjoy this selection of mostly random links! If you find something useful please let us know!</p>

            <% data.picks.each do |number, picks| %>
              <% episode = sitemap.find_resource_by_path("podcast/#{number}.html") %>
              <% if episode %>
                <h3 class="posttitle_typesome">
                  <%= link_to episode.title, episode %>
                </h3>
                <%= partial :picks_by_guest, locals: { picks: picks } %>
              <% end %>
            <% end %>
        </div>
    </article>

</main>
